             separates module lifecycle management from
            , which handles attribute-based discovery.
            The two systems are complementary:


Attribute discovery ([DataSource]) — single-class registration

Module loading — multi-capability, grouped registration per provider

            Typical usage:

            var loader = new ProviderModuleLoader();
            var report = await loader.LoadFromAssembliesAsync(services, registry, ct,
                typeof(AlpacaProviderModule).Assembly);
